IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. SimpleDataItemsDemo.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 EMPLOYEE-INFO.
   05 EMPLOYEE-NAME   PIC X(30).
   05 EMPLOYEE-AGE    PIC 99.
   05 EMPLOYEE-SALARY PIC 9(5)V99.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
BEGIN-PROCESS.
    DISPLAY "Enter Employee Name: ".
    ACCEPT EMPLOYEE-NAME.

    DISPLAY "Enter Employee Age: ".
    ACCEPT EMPLOYEE-AGE.

    DISPLAY "Enter Employee Salary: ".
    ACCEPT EMPLOYEE-SALARY.

    DISPLAY "Employee Details:".
    DISPLAY "Name: ", EMPLOYEE-NAME.
    DISPLAY "Age: ", EMPLOYEE-AGE.
    DISPLAY "Salary: $", EMPLOYEE-SALARY.

    STOP RUN.
